title: Anymore
lyrics:
I close my eyes
Enter a warmth
My heart beating slow
So soft and dark
I talk to you

I talk to you



I want it to be

All around me

I'll think about it

'Till I am empty



I get undone

I get undone



So hollow and true

It's got me weak

I wonder if you

Think about me



Not anymore

Not anymore



My head sunk and swayed

All down the hill

We cut through the night

Our bodies so still



And I let it go

I let it go



I thought to you

I thought to you

I thought to you

I thought to you
